org.spongepowered.api.data.value.immutable

Interface ImmutableWeightedEntityCollectionValue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseValue<WeightedCollection<WeightedEntity>>, ImmutableCollectionValue<WeightedEntity,WeightedCollection<WeightedEntity>,ImmutableWeightedEntityCollectionValue,WeightedEntityCollectionValue>, ImmutableValue<WeightedCollection<WeightedEntity>>, ImmutableWeightedCollectionValue<WeightedEntity,ImmutableWeightedEntityCollectionValue,WeightedEntityCollectionValue>

    public interface ImmutableWeightedEntityCollectionValue
extends ImmutableWeightedCollectionValue<WeightedEntity,ImmutableWeightedEntityCollectionValue,WeightedEntityCollectionValue>
    Represents an ImmutableWeightedEntityCollectionValue that uses a WeightedEntity as the element type. This is mainly used to simplify various ImmutableCollectionValues to use the WeightedCollection type.

        ImmutableWeightedEntityCollectionValue with(EntityType entityType,
                                            Collection<DataManipulator<?,?>> entityData)
